data.description: Incredibly spacious living room opens into a big kitchen and dining nook! Enclosed patio is perfect for enjoying Florida sun while ignoring Florida heat! Behind the home you'll find a fenced in garden ready for growing. Heading upstairs you're greeted with a massive walk in closet in the hallway and a linen closet flanked by the large bedrooms! This two bedroom setup is ideal for investment as the design is identical on both sides with a single vanity, flanked by the bathroom and walk in closet!Call and schedule a showing today so we can hand you keys tomorrow! Dimensions to be updated.
